definition: to pass on/to spread/to transmit/to infect/to transfer/to circulate/to conduct (electricity)

sentences.english: The emperor passes decree, enrol emperor's son-in-law than seesaw.
sentences.chinese: 皇帝傳旨，比蹺蹺板招駙馬。

sentences.english: The Jade Emperor sent for God Erh-lang.
sentences.chinese: 玉帝聞言，即差神使前去傳旨。
